<p>Molly E. Holzschlag is the prolific author of over 35 books which have helped to define standards and best practices over the years, including <i>The Zen of CSS Design: Visual Enlightenment for the Web</i>, written with Dave Shea. Molly is actively involved in various W3C working groups and talks at prestigious events around the globe. Her clients include the likes of AOL, Adobe Systems, Auto-by-Tel, BBC, eBay, Fidelity, Microsoft, MSN, Progressive Insurance, Yahoo!</p>
<p>Molly has <a href="http://www.molly.com/">a website</a>, and a Twitter account <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/mollydotcom">@mollydotcom</a>.</p>